\begin_layout Subsection
Space Lattices or Bravais Lattices
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Points in 3-D space can be arranged such that each has identical surroundings
 in 14 ways.
 These are divided into 
\series bold
7 Crystal Systems.
\end_layout

