\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Crystal defects
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $\therefore$
\end_inset

Use angle integrated peak intensities to find relative values of 
\begin_inset Formula $|F|^{2}$
\end_inset

 (then compare to calculated 
