\begin_inset Caption Standard

\begin_layout Plain Layout
Rotating-crystal pattern of a quartz crystal (hexagonal) rotated about its
 c axis.
 Filtered copper radiation.
 (The streaks are due to white radiation not removed by the filter.) (Courtesy
 of B.E.
 Warren.)
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

